{
  "body": "<html><body><div id=\"block-ti-west-content\">\n<section class=\"webinar-detail\">\n<div class=\"webinar-hero-banner hero__container hero__container--text-dark hero__container--no-overlay hero__container--color\">\n<div class=\"container container--max-width\">\n<h1 class=\"webinar-title\">\n<span>Annuities in Focus: Abuse, Accountability, and Advancement</span>\n</h1>\n<span data-item-id=\"81083\" data-price=\"49.00\" data-product=\"Annuities in Focus: Abuse, Accountability, and Advancement\" data-react-component-id=\"add-to-cart\">\n<button class=\"btn btn--primary btn--disabled\">Add to Cart -\t\t\t\t\t\t&amp;dollar;49.00</button>\n</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width container__flex u-padding-top\">\n<span class=\"u-text-uppercase badge badge--dark badge--icon\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"u-icon-calendar-dims\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use xlink:href=\"#calendar\"></use>\n</svg>\n<div><time datetime=\"2026-03-17T15:00:00Z\">Mar. 17 2026 11:00 AM EDT</time>\n</div>\n</span>\n<div class=\"webinar-block u-margin-bottom\">\n<div>\n<div class=\"webinar-description u-padding-bottom\">\n<p>Annuities sit at the center of some of the most controversial moments in insurance and financial services. Explores how questionable sales practices, aggressive marketing, product complexity, and regulatory action shaped today’s suitability and best interest framework. Study the abuses that harmed clients, the conflicts that eroded public confidence, and the reforms designed to correct them. Real-world examples reveal how ethical professionals can apply these lessons to improve recommendations, strengthen communication, and operate with greater accountability.</p><ul><li><span>Standard Webinar Price: $49.00</span></li><li><span>CEU Unlimited Subscriber Price: Included in your subscription.</span><ul><li><em>*CEU Unlimited subscriber webinar discount will be reflected in the checkout process. <span style=\"color:#A31E2C;\"><strong>No